{"id":370514,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":11}],"page":"1","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"331","ytitle":"","mtitle":"钢铁工人之歌","ftitle":"","authors":["陈衍良"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟囱平地起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨一阵下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨后春笋长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟囱平地起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉耸云霄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(上钢一厂)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗和钢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口里唱山歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干活真快乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一点汗珠一吨钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗滴越多钢越多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(上钢一厂)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雷一声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰动上钢厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双反成绩大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一季度打了漂亮仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"产量高，质量强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(上钢一厂)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱大跃进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百花怒放迎新春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风吹遍上钢城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命干劲热如火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双反运动大跃进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找关键，动脑筋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全厂职工一条心!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产热潮高又高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁勇士称英豪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘风破浪大跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生龙活虎比干劲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摆擂台，攻碉堡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产纪录日日新!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长空放光明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万人大会传捷音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年生产一年成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群英誓师提保证。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你挑战，我应战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓足干劲比先进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进军号角响云霄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷霆万钧气势威，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命火花万丈高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四面八方大跃进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学先进，比干劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进跃进再跃进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(上钢一厂陈衍良)"}]}